{"tid":785251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港賴以成功之道是什麼？","createTime":"2018-08-19T05:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T17:18:58.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c1b4aca176c28233a09a0cd2f3bd69ba255681","tid":785251,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港以<strong>《美國-香港政策法》</strong>賦予的獨特地位成為國際經濟、貿易、財經中心，成績有目共睹，亦得來不易。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n美國海軍維護太平洋印度洋航行安全，香港海軍零成本，專心做轉口貿易即可。<br />\n<br />\n聯繫匯率制度確保香港幣值穩定，有利營商。<br />\n<br />\n與英法高相容性的普通法制度。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f4eb7d6a9180e7cbb16bd6e8c9d4e1d134a8f0","tid":785251,"uid":103127,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aadabd1b961229a0d4ea762ee5ef903c84c45201","tid":785251,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:11:53.000Z","msg":"工時長，人工平，人口密度高"},{"pid":"f4fba2057ac81b35711b6786ca2d676e77f3923a","tid":785251,"uid":99048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:12:34.000Z","msg":"仲有免費ot 唔洗錢"},{"pid":"b9b063246f998a320998613271e926211bd43772","tid":785251,"uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:12:57.000Z","msg":"支那仆街"},{"pid":"76970dd2be5c81a5f28d83eab991cc2e3f36f356","tid":785251,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:14:11.000Z","msg":"英國佬"},{"pid":"c4ddda82dec19b596353bc78d1726e9b3e3f230e","tid":785251,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T05:14:29.000Z","msg":"口甜舌滑<br />\n<br />\n一個樓盤400呎都可以叫豪宅"},{"pid":"69238ccd138b7afc280c39cf5b607f5105f9680c","tid":785251,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited